      • canLoad

        boolean canLoad(UnloadedProject project)
        Checks if the module can load the project This is used if the original module for the project can not be found anymore, there is a chance that the project can still be used. The project will not have your module's id and will throw an exception if you run Project.getExpectedModule()
        Parameters:
        project - The project to check
        Returns:
        If your module can load the project
